						<div class="postbody">I suppose you could use (zp,x) as pointers to pointers. (Or rather, to get the starting offset within a pointer table). But I would still prefer to use (zp), y or some other mode for that.<br /><br />I made it pretty clear on my blog that I don't like (zp, x) mode, and don't use it.</div>

					
